Package it.unipi.dii.lsmsd.pokeMongo.userInterface

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AddRemovePokemon
    It initializes the scene, only visible to an admin user, for removing and adding pokemon.
    AnalyticsScene
    Scene related to the analytics (admin specific).
    CatchEmAll
    Scene related to the catch of pokemon.
    CurrentUI
    CurrentUI handles the scene showed to the user
    CurrentUITest  
    Friends  
    HomePage
    HomePage is the principal scene showed to the user.
    LogIn
    Class scene related to the Log In page
    MusicPlayer
    Class dedicated to handle the music in the scene.
    Pokedex
    Class scene related to the Podekex
    PokeScene
    PokeScene is the root class of the scene classes, a new scene must extends this one or one of its children.
    PokeSceneWithBlastoiseCharizard
    This class should be used to be extended by scenes that want Blastoice and Charizard in the background.
    PokeSceneWithHeader
    This class should be used to be extended by scenes that want the header containing the username and the number of pokeball hold (this one only for normal user).
    PokeSceneWithHeaderAndAggregateBlastoiseCharizard
    This class create a sort of double inheritance because it instantiates a PokeSceneWithBlastoiseCharizard.
    PokeSceneWithHeaderAndBackButton
    This class should be used to be extended by scenes that want the header containing the username and the number of pokeball hold (this one only for normal user), and the back button for coming back to the HomePage.
    PokeSceneWithTitle
    This class should be used to be extended by scenes that want the title PokeMongo
    RankingScene
    This class is used to display the Node concerning the Rankings.
    RemoveUserScene
    This is allow available to the admin user
    Settings
    This class is used to display the Node concerning the Settings.
    SignUp
    This class is used to display the Node concerning the Settings.
    TeamScene
    This class is used to display the Node concerning the Team.
